      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(SemVer o)
        Compare this semVer object to another given object. Comparisons are based on instance major value, then minor, then patch, and finally the pre rekease values. Values are calculated im ascending numeric order for integer values, and lexicographically for String values
        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable<SemVer>
        Returns:
        int - a value less than 0 if object 1 comes before object 2, greater than 0 if object 1 comes after object 2, and 0 if they are equal
